=Description=

"In this episode, I am hosting Stelio Verzera, the founder of Cocoon Projects - a company that is simply different. For the past 10 years, Stelio experimented and succeeded with a totally new type of organization, one that anyone can join (yes, there is no selection process carried out by Cocoon Pro, just one carried out by the future collaborator), that promotes full transparency, trust and incentivizes the right outcomes.
Besides Cocoon and the LiquidO Framework, we also touch on the current state of organizations, the effects of the pandemic, the future of organizations, and his latest project."

